entry.lex: The 1 Decembrie 1918 University is located in Alba lulia, Alba. Its Latin name is "Universitas Apulensis" and its nickname is "Uab".

entry.lex: The AWH Engineering College is located in Kuttikkattoor, Kerala and it has 250 academic staff. Kerala has Mahe, India to its northwest.
